# Security

Follow `web-security` (`.cursor/skills/web-security/SKILL.md`).

- Validate all external input at server boundaries
- Secrets in `$env/static/private` only — never client imports
- No `{@html}` with unsanitised content
- `.env` gitignored; document keys in `.env.example`
